Super Splits
Mac Application for timing Super Metroid speed runs, and providing per-room splits.

Super Splits can be used both for timing live runs, as well as collecting room timing information from videos of past runs.

http://supersplits.com/

For more information about speed-running, see:
http://speedrunslive.com/gamelist/game.php?game=supermetroid
http://speeddemosarchive.com/SuperMetroid.html

Thanks to Spike Black for all his help testing:
http://www.twitch.tv/spike2071
https://twitter.com/#!/SpikeBlack2071
